{"article_id":"xkWpmPR4CvqbITpq","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez and Sen. Ed Markey hold a news conference for their proposed \" Green New Deal \" on Capitol Hill , February 7 , 2019 .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"( Jonathan Ernst/Reuters )","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"It ' s not a very serious proposal ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"but the worldview behind it is dangerous .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"On Thursday , Representative Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"( D. , N.Y. )","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"and Senator Ed Markey","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"( D. , Mass . )","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"introduced what many news outlets described as \" legislation \" for the Green New Deal , a wildly ambitious plan","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"to eliminate the American fossil-fuel industry within a decade or so .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"It ' s worth noting that it ' s not legislation","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"as people normally understand the term .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"It ' s a resolution","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"titled \" Recognizing the duty of the Federal Government","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"to create a Green New Deal. \"","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"In other words ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"even if it passed","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"- a considerable if -","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"nothing would really happen .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi isn ' t taking it too seriously .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"She didn ' t put Ocasio-Cortez on the new Select Committee on the Climate Crisis ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"and","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"when asked about the resolution ,","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"she was dismissive .","depth":14},{"id":24,"text":"\" It will be one of several or maybe many suggestions","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"that we receive , \"","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"Pelosi said .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"\" The green dream or whatever they call it ,","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"nobody knows","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"what it is ,","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"but they ' re for it ,","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"right ? \"","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"I bring this up for the simple reason","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that a lot of people on the left and the right have every incentive","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"to make this thing a much bigger deal","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"than it is .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Still ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"given that almost everyone","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"running for the Democratic presidential nomination","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"feels obliged to say","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"they ' re for it ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"it ' s worth taking somewhat seriously .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"This raises the first of several problems :","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"It ' s not a very serious proposal .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"The goal is to eliminate the fossil-fuel industry over a decade","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"and , perversely , phase out nuclear power over a slightly longer period .","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"All of the jobs","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"dependent on these industries","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"would be replaced by government-guaranteed jobs .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"\" We set a goal","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"to get to net-zero , rather than zero emissions , in 10 years , \"","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"the backers explain in an outline ,","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"\" because we aren ' t sure","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"that we ' ll be able to fully get rid of farting cows and airplanes that fast ,","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"but we think","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"we can ramp up renewable manufacturing and power production ,","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"retrofit every building in America ,","depth":17},{"id":57,"text":"build the smart grid ,","depth":18},{"id":58,"text":"overhaul transportation and agriculture ,","depth":19},{"id":59,"text":"plant lots of trees","depth":20},{"id":60,"text":"and restore our ecosystem","depth":20},{"id":61,"text":"to get to net-zero . \"","depth":16},{"id":62,"text":"Well , at least the plan isn ' t too ambitious .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"Retrofitting \" every building in America \" can be done in 10 years ,","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"but eliminating all the gassy cows will take a bit longer .","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"Maybe we ' ll move them all to Hawaii ,","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"which with the near-abolition of airplanes will be effectively cut off from America anyway .","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"Even if you take these goals seriously ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"as a practical matter it ' s a fantasy","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"masquerading as green virtue-signaling .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"But it ' s a fantasy","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"based on a worldview","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"that should be treated seriously","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"because it ' s so dangerous .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"NPR ' s Steve Inskeep asked Ocasio-Cortez","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"whether she was comfortable with the \" massive government intervention \"","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"critics say","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"is required by such an undertaking .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"\" We have tried their approach for 40 years , \"","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"Ocasio-Cortez replied .","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"\" For 40 years we have tried to let the private sector take care of this .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"They said ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"' We got this ,","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"we can do this ,","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"the forces of the market are going to force us to innovate. '","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"Except for the fact that there ' s a little thing in economics","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"called externalities .","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"And what that means is that a corporation can dump pollution in the river","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"and they don ' t have to pay for it ,","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"and taxpayers have to pay . \"","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"The fascinating thing is","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"that Ocasio-Cortez thinks","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"this is actually true .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"Thanks to the government intervention","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"known as the Clean Water Act","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"and other regulations ,","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"corporations can ' t pollute waterways .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"Ironically , the only entities","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"that can pollute with impunity","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"are government agencies such as the EPA ,","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"which did precisely that in Colorado in 2015 .","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"Closer to home , ExxonMobil has spent millions","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"cleaning up Newtown Creek ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"which happens to run through Ocasio-Cortez ' s native Brooklyn , close to her district .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"Ironically , the city of New York is still allowed to pollute the creek","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"whenever there ' s a heavy rainfall .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Even if Ocasio-Cortez was speaking figuratively in her talk of \" externalities , \"","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"the larger point remains .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"The free market hasn ' t been given free rein ,","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"and over the last 40 years the free market and government regulations alike have made laudable environmental progress .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"In 2017 , the U.S. had the largest reductions of CO2 emissions in the world for the ninth time this century .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"Rather than celebrate and build on that reality ,","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"the Green New Dealers would rather embrace their fantasies","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"- and waste a lot of time and money in the process .","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"Something to Consider","depth":4},{"id":115,"text":"If you enjoyed this article ,","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"we have a proposition for you :","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"Join NRPLUS .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Members get all of our content","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"( including the magazine ) ,","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"no paywalls or content meters , an advertising-minimal experience , and unique access to our writers and editors","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"( conference calls , social-media groups , etc. ) .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"And importantly , NRPLUS members help keep NR going .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"Consider it ?","depth":5},{"id":124,"text":"If you enjoyed this article ,","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"and were stimulated by its contents ,","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"we have a proposition for you :","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"Join NRPLUS .","depth":5},{"id":128,"text":"LEARN MORE","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":257,"left":130,"right":256,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":130,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":241,"right":255,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":241,"left":131,"right":240,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":232,"right":239,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":232,"left":168,"right":231,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":145,"right":167,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":136,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":132,"right":135,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":132,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity